high_descs: Head rotate and turn left to the safe.
Turn right to the lettuce.
Turn left to the diningtable and pick the cabbage and rotate the bedroom inside.
Turn right and walk towards the diningtable.
Turn left and turn left to the dresser.
Place the lettuce on the table and turn right to the stairs.
Turn right to the bedroom and pick the cabbage on the diningtable.
Turn left and place the lettuce on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: To place the lettuce on the diningtable.

high_descs: Go straight in the passage take left and enter in the bed room near by the safe.
Open the locker and pick the lettuce from it.
Take the cabbage from the diningtable and pass through a passage straight and enter left the kitchen room table.
Place the lettuce on the diningtable.
Walk away from kitchen and take right and enter the bed room dresser.
Pick another lettuce from the bed room table.
Walk away from bed room  and take right  and enter the kitchen diningtable.
Place the second lettuce on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Collect two lettuce and place it on the diningtable.

high_descs: Go ahead, turn right. When you reach the safe, turn right. Reach the lamp. Turn left. Reach the safe.
Grab the lettuce.
Turn around. To approach the diningtable. Turn to the right. When you reach the end of the diningtable, turn left. When you reach the end, turn right. Go forward. Turn left. Go forward, turn left.
Place the lettuce on the right side of the diningtable at the end.
Turn left, move forward. Turn right. Move forward, as you leave the room, turn right. Reach the end of the corridor, turn right. Move forward and turn left. Approach the dresser. Turn left.
Grab the lettuce.
Gore to the left. Go forward. Turn right, turn left. Continue, at the end of the corridor turn left. When you reach the wall, turn left. When you reach the diningtable, turn left.
Place the lettuce on the right side of the other lettuce on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Find two Lettuce, place them on the DiningTable.
